name: Wearing the First 2048 OBJKTs
description: Tywen Kelly | Instagram: @tywensnotes | A real-time GLSL shader that samples the first 2048 minted NFTs on hic et nunc and re-places them against my desk webcam. I try and "grab" the NFTs, and in doing so I reveal more NFTs. (Data scraped from hic et nunc using Mario Klingemann's python script.)
